The SAMI (*.smi) [[subtitle]] format is a '''rare''' {{HTML}}-format with startframes given for each subtitle.

Example:
<pre>
<TITLE>Title of film
<STYLE TYPE="text/css">
                          <blank line>
<BODY>
                          <blank line>
<SYNC Start=30886>
Oh no!  The eggs are hatching!
                          <blank line>
<SYNC Start=34037>
Wait, never mind.  I was hallucinating.
</pre>

